        Parameters:

        chan - string containing the NSCL
        lt - channel latitude (negative, south)
        lg - channel longitude (negative, west)
        el - channel elevation (not used in FK analysis)
        cr - channel corrections factor (not used in FK analysis)
        us - channel usage: =0, do not use
        parent - The EdgeThread for any logging
